# crAPI uses the upstream OWASP Helm chart, vendored at apps/crapi/chart/.
# It is deployed by the Argo CD "crapi" Application (see argocd/lab-apps),
# which renders this chart with apps/crapi/values.yaml as a $values overlay.
#
# Refresh the chart with:  task crapi:chart:update
#
# Reasoning for vendoring (vs fetching at deploy time):
#   - Air-gapped lab runs work without internet
#   - Reproducible: a given commit always deploys the same chart
#   - Bad upstream changes can't break the lab silently
#   - Updates are intentional: pull, diff, test, commit
